metadata.name: Du-Rag
metadata.description:
Du-Rag photographed in LES Skatepark shortly after nollie flipping bank to bank with a Thrasher t-shirt over his head, only revealing his eyes.

Alex spent the month of August skating, documenting and capturing the characters, atmosphere and scenes in LES skatepark. Located under the Manhattan Bridge in Chinatown NYC, the skatepark draws an eclectic mix of local characters and skateboarders.
